						<summary>

						<p>Same wall.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Tribhº Vīragaṇḍagōpāladēva: Year 5 = 1296 A.D. (?)</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription records a gift of a <hi rend="italic">sandhi</hi> lamp to the temple of the god Tiruviṟkōlamuḍaiya-nāyanār of Kūvam <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Tiyāgasamudranallūr, by a woman named Umaiyāḻvāṉ, wife of Paṇḍaraṅkiḻān, Tiruvaraṅgamuḍaiyān. This gift was accepted by three people, whose names are given, who had agreed to carry out the object of the gift. </p>						

						</summary>
